creator: FayvitApp
descriptionHtml:
Fayvit is a mobile app that is dedicated to providing the most authentic and reliable way to discover people’s favourite places and experiences, both locally and around the world!

With Fayvit you can:
1. Post and organize travel experiences in one place
2. Easily discover new places to go and things to go
3. Follow friends and like-minded users to get the most authentic and relevant content.

Don’t waste time sifting through sponsored ads, a myriad of blogs, reviews or recommendations from “experts.” Fayvit won’t give you paid for 5 Star Reviews, just straight fayvs!
descriptionShort: Discover best places to go and things to do no matter where you're with Fayvit!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
* Discover search optimisation based user’s location and “Everyone” filter has been removed.
* Fayvs on the discover feed are only fayvs that have not been added to a collection.
* Signup - Mobile number mandatory field is added and verification flow has been done.
* Username - Username creation flow implemented when user login using facebook.
* UTC Server Time - Timezone has updated as per the device time to show created time of Fayv/Collections.
